[[Category:pages to sort]][[cdo:10 nguŏk 24 hô̤ (nùng-lĭk)]] [[zh-min-nan:10 goe̍h 24 ji̍t (kū-le̍k)]] [[zh-yue:十月廿四]] {{Lunisolar October}} '''October 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1855 AD|ja|1855th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 3|ja|12月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Nagasaki Naval Training Center|ja|長崎海軍伝習所|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is established.
== Births == * {{ill|Genbun|ja|元文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1740 AD|ja|1740th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shuraku Sugae|ja|朱楽菅江|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a writer of comic verses and parodies (d. {{ill|1800 AD|ja|1800th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Annai|ja|安永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1773 AD|ja|1773rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Harunori|ja|徳川治紀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 7th lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (d. {{ill|1816 AD|ja|1816th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛弘|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1011 AD|ja|1011th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Reisō Tennō|ja|冷泉天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 63rd {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|950 AD|ja|950th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1708 AD|ja|1708th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Seki Takakazu|ja|関孝和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a mathematician and the progenitor of {{ill|Wasan|ja|和算|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1642 AD|ja|1642nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
