{{Lunisolar October}} 
'''October 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1855 AD|ja|1855th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 3|ja|12月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Nagasaki Naval Training Center|ja|長崎海軍伝習所|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  is established.

== Births ==
