* {{ill|Annai|ja|安永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1773 AD|ja|1773rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Harunori|ja|徳川治紀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 7th lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  (d. {{ill|1816 AD|ja|1816th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
