* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1708 AD|ja|1708th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Seki Takakazu|ja|関孝和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a mathematician and the progenitor of {{ill|Wasan|ja|和算|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  (born {{ill|1642 AD|ja|1642nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).


