{{Lunisolar October}} 
'''October 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}}  day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1855 AD|ja|1855th year}}  {{ill|December 3|ja|12月3日}} ) – The {{ill|Nagasaki Naval Training Center|ja|長崎海軍伝習所}}  is established.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Genbun|ja|元文}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1740 AD|ja|1740th year}}  {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日}} ) – {{ill|Shuraku Sugae|ja|朱楽菅江}} , a writer of comic verses and parodies (d. {{ill|1800 AD|ja|1800th year}} ).
* {{ill|Annai|ja|安永}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1773 AD|ja|1773rd year}}  {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Harunori|ja|徳川治紀}} , the 7th lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain}}  (d. {{ill|1816 AD|ja|1816th year}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kankō|ja|寛弘}}  8th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}}  {{ill|1011 AD|ja|1011th year}}  {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日}} ) – {{ill|Reisō Tennō|ja|冷泉天皇}} , the 63rd {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇}}  (born {{ill|950 AD|ja|950th year}} ).
* {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1708 AD|ja|1708th year}}  {{ill|December 5|ja|12月5日}} ) – {{ill|Seki Takakazu|ja|関孝和}} , a mathematician and the progenitor of {{ill|Wasan|ja|和算}}  (born {{ill|1642 AD|ja|1642nd year}} ).


