== Births == * {{ill|Genbun|ja|元文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1740 AD|ja|1740th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shuraku Sugae|ja|朱楽菅江|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a writer of comic verses and parodies (d. {{ill|1800 AD|ja|1800th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Annai|ja|安永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1773 AD|ja|1773rd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Harunori|ja|徳川治紀|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 7th lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (d. {{ill|1816 AD|ja|1816th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
