== Births == * [[:en:Genbun|Genbun]] 5th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1740|1740 AD]] [[:en:December 12|December 12]] ) – {{ill|Shuraku Sugae|ja|朱楽菅江|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shuraku Sugae|qq=}} , a writer of comic verses and parodies (d. [[:en:1800|1800 AD]] ). * {{ill|Annai|ja|安永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Annai|qq=}} 2nd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1773|1773 AD]] [[:en:December 7|December 7]] ) – [[:en:Tokugawa Harutoshi|Tokugawa Harunori]] , the 7th lord of the {{ill|Mito Domain|1=Mito Domain|2=ja|3=水戸藩|ja|Mito Domain|1=Mito Domain|2=ja|3=水戸藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mito Domain|qq=}} (d. [[:en:1816|1816 AD]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Kankō|Kankō]] 8th Year ( [[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1011|1011 AD]] [[:en:November 21|November 21]] ) – [[:en:Emperor Reizei|Reisō Tennō]] , the 63rd [[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor]] (born [[:en:950|950 AD]] ). * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 5th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1708|1708 AD]] [[:en:December 5|December 5]] ) – [[:en:Seki Takakazu|Seki Takakazu]] , a mathematician and the progenitor of [[:en:Japanese mathematics|Wasan]] (born [[:en:1642|1642 AD]] ).
